    {
      "id": 171833,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "The researcher reported that a login form of a Sony website was vulnerable to a blind SQL injection. The researcher was able to use the blind SQL injection to enable xp_cmdshell functionality on the database and then run system commands. The output from the system commands was then obtained via DNS-based exfiltration.",
